<html metal:use-macro="context/@@main_template/master">
    <body>
        <div metal:fill-slot="main">
          <h1 class="exception">
            Sorry, a system error occurred
          </h1>
          <p>
            If you were just adding or changing something,
            ShipIt probably hasn&#8217;t recorded those changes.
          </p>
          <h2>What you can do</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <p>
                If you entered a lot of text
                that you don&#8217;t want to lose,
                go Back, copy the text,
                and paste it into a text file.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p>
                While you&#8217;re there,
                copy the URL of the page too.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p>
              <a href="https://launchpad.net/malone/products/shipit">Report the bug</a>,
                after checking that it isn&#8217;t reported already.
                In your bug report,
                include the <abbr>URL</abbr> of the page you were
                on, and what you tried to do.
              </p>
              <tal:block condition="view/show_tracebacks">
                <p>
                  Also include this debugging information:
                </p>
                <div tal:content="structure view/htmltext | default">
                    HTML rendering of error should go here.
                </div>
              </tal:block>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            Thanks for helping us improve, and sorry for the inconvenience.
          </p>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
